(b) William7 b. 1767-12-02, d. 1838-09-24, m. Mary Grover;
(c) Roeloff b. ?, m. Elizabeth Johnson;
(d) Jane bap. 1772-02-23 Old Tennent Church, prob. d.y.;
(e) Elsie bap. 1774-04-24 Old Tennent Church, prob. d.y.;
(f) Deborah b. ?, m. Zebulon Stout of Hopewell, N.J.;
(g) Mary b. ?.

